-- Media Capital's TVI Widens Lead in Portugal's TV Ratings for This Month
-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 2010-09-30T12:16:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/media-capital-s-tvi-widens-lead-in-portugal-s-tv-ratings-for-this-month.html
Media Capital SGPS SA’s TVI widened
its lead over rival broadcasters in television audience ratings,
through September 29, in Portugal.  TVI had 34.8 percent of viewers of the four free-to-air
stations, while state-owned RTP1 had 28.8 percent and Impresa
SGPS SA’s SIC had 28.6 percent, TVI said today in an e-mailed
statement. In August, TVI had a 1.5 percentage-point lead.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anabela Reis at 
 areis1@bloomberg.net  